  "name": "Deploy - Franchise Connect (Head Office)",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"deploy-franchise-connect-head-office\">Deploy - Franchise Connect (Head Office)</h1>\n<p><span><span>This article explains how to deploy a Franchise Connect database once a signed contract has been received and paid for:</span></span></p>\n<p><span>Create New Head Office Database</span></p>\n<p><img alt=\"rtaImage (38).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powZOEAY.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powZOEAY.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powZOEAY.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powZOEAY.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powZOEAY.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powZOEAY.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powZOEAY.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powZOEAY.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>1. Login to <a href=\"\">MGMT</a></p>\n<p>2. Navigate to <strong>HeadOffice &gt; New HO</strong></p>\n<p>3. Enter details as follows:</p>\n<p><em>Site Name:</em> Company Trading As name (no spaces and CamelCase)</p>\n<p><em>Site Type:</em> select 'ClientSite' from dropdown</p>\n<p><em>Server Set:</em> select default from dropdown menu</p>\n<p><em>ARI Industry/Vertical:</em> select appropriate retail vertical from dropdown</p>\n<p>4. Click on <strong>Create HO Site </strong>button</p>\n<p>5. Ensure that a success message is returned - if process fails advise the development team</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span>Linking up databases to </span></p>\n<p><img alt=\"rtaImage (39).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powa6EAA.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powa6EAA.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powa6EAA.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powa6EAA.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powa6EAA.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powa6EAA.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powa6EAA.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powa6EAA.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>1. When a database is ready to be connected to the Head Office Module go to <strong>HeadOffice &gt; HO Site List</strong></p>\n<p>2. Filter by company name in <strong>Admin Link</strong></p>\n<p>3. Clink on <strong><span>Edit Members</span></strong> this will bring up a popup screen where you can select the databases to associate:</p>\n<p><strong> </strong><img alt=\"rtaImage (40).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powaBEAQ.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powaBEAQ.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powaBEAQ.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powaBEAQ.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powaBEAQ.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powaBEAQ.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powaBEAQ.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powaBEAQ.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>4. Scroll down the <strong>Non Members </strong>list until you have found the database name to add and then click on the arrow facing right icon and it will move this database name into the <strong>Members</strong> list.</p>\n<p>5. Once you have repeated this process as necessary click on the <strong>Submit button</strong></p>\n<p>6. Back in the Head Office Sites list you will see that the <strong>Member Count </strong>has increased accordingly</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span>Zendesk - Sending the email </span></p>\n<p><img alt=\"rtaImage (41).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powaGEAQ.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powaGEAQ.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powaGEAQ.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powaGEAQ.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powaGEAQ.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powaGEAQ.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powaGEAQ.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powaGEAQ.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>1. Add a new ticket</p>\n<p>2. Add the email address for the contact on the solutions agreement</p>\n<p>3. Select the macro <strong>Implementation &gt; Deployment &gt; Franchise Connect</strong></p>\n<p>4. Replace <em>ClientName, password, linked db names</em> with the relevant information for the client</p>\n<p>5. Submit the ticket as Solved</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>For Franchisee deployment, see also <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Franchise-Connect-Franchisee-Configuration\" title=\"Franchise Connect - Franchisee Configuration\">Franchise Connect - Franchisee Configuration</a></p>",
